title: VSO ConvertXtoDVD 2.99.18.970 Registered Setup
description:
VSO ConvertXtoDVD 2.99.18.970 Registered Setup

What&#039;s new in this Version:
Add support for 2 new video format: 
VP7 and VC1 Advanced profile
- TrueMotion VP70 Unsupported video stream on ConvertXToDVD
- Add support for Windows Movie Maker video

The Setup and Program Files:
- Server check removed
- Registered
- Unnecessary Windows Registry Entries: Digital River, SoftwarePassport resellers (nexway,01net,...) cleaned up / removed from installation script

 
Remark:
BitDefender Antivirus detect the exe packer as virus Packer.XComp.A
You are safe to ignore it. It&#039;s a false positive by all applications packed with Packer Compressor XComp098, XComp097. I don&#039;t let me force to use other packers such as UPX or PE Compact only because some Virus scanner don&#039;t support XComp to scan inside the packed/compressed files.
